translations: 用精神分析疗法治疗分析

sentences.translation: 不要对我来心里分析这一套，你这个傻子！

sentences.sentence: And you can imagine how many trees would have been slaughtered in the past few months as journalists tried to psychoanalyze Master Wayne's scoring drought.
sentences.translation: 并且你能够想到，随着记者视图分析鲁尼的进球荒，在过去的几个月里有多少树木要被砍伐。
